once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey on a berry tree, which was on the banks of the 
river.In the same forest, there lived a Crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came to the
banks of the river.The kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back to 
monkey for more fruits,as he loved them.as days passed by,the crocodile and the monkey became
good friends.